Installation of prometheus.
Install prometheus Tested on minikube.
1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9 helm repo add prometheus-community https://prometheus-community.github.io/helm-charts helm repo update kubectl create namespace monitoring helm install prometheus prometheus-community/prometheus \ --namespace monitoring \ --set alertmanager.persistentVolume.storageClass=&#34;standard&#34; \ --set server.persistentVolume.storageClass=&#34;standard&#34;
